text: Theil-sur-Vanne is a former commune. It is found in the Yonne department in the center of France. On 1 January 2016, it was merged into the new commune of Les Vallées-de-la-Vanne.Arrêté préfectoral 15 December 2015 ==References== *INSEE Category:Former communes in Yonne
title: Theil-sur-Vanne
